"""Develop a program that reads a four-digit integer from the user and displays the sum
of the digits in the number. For example, if the user enters 3141 then your program
should display 3+1+4+1=9."""

number = int(input("Introduce a whole number: "))
string = str(number)
sum = int(string[0]) + int(string[1]) + int(string[2]) + int(string[3])
print("The sum of the digits of the integer {} is {}.".format(number,sum))
